title: Sul Ross hosts business regulatory roundtable (Sul Ross State University)
text: ( Source : Sul Ross State University ) Alpine small business representatives, including Lawrence Neu , Mountain Zone Cable Systems (right photo), participated in a panel roundtable, 'The Regulatory World of Business in Alpine, TX ,' held Oct. 13
